# in R

## edit qmd file `_parameters in R.qmd`

![](images/paste-2.png)

## render qmd file with parameters input

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(quarto)
quarto_render("_parameters in R.qmd"
,output_file='R.html'
,execute_params = list(name='new me',key=9999))
```
:::
